        "timestamp": "2017-09-28 09:55:59.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi Marcus,\n\nWhen I tested this template found following output.\n{\n  \"l2-dci-connect\": {\n    \"id\": \"\"Id1\"\",\n    \"name\": \"\"Name1\"\",\n    \"network_id\": \"\"NetId1\"\",\n    \"evpn_irts\": [\"[\n\t\"100:1\",\n\t\"200:1\"\n]\"],\n    \"evpn_erts\": [\"[\n\t\"100:2\",\n\t\"200:2\"\n]\"],\n    \"vni\": \"\"1\"\"\n  }\n}\n\n-- it has extra Quotes around value, also extra Square bracket around list (kindly correct me if the way I am testing is not right)\n-- values are specific to l3-dci, as per recent information we need to support l3-dci and l2-dci together.\n\nHave added a patch with testcase, https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/16317/, kindly review and see if it make sense.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      }
